            <p class="pr-card__title">I check this before I check my phone now.</p>
            <p class="pr-card__text">Which is saying something lol. Pushed through workouts all week feeling off — scores red every day. Finally rested. Wish I'd listened sooner.</p>
            <footer class="pr-card__footer">
